div.div:
OPTIONS
parent: where to create the game
url: where to look for imgs and sounds
submit: submit -function
sendAnswer: save answer
data: game settings
DATA
question: target value (can be a calculation too)
options: which numbers are in use
operation: how to combine numbers
(addition, subtraction, multiplication, division)
startValue: start combining from this number
theme: which theme to use
Optional settings
lifes: how many lifes
time: how long you can try to solve the problem
useTimer: if timer is used or not
